{"tid":1555422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位公務員可唔可以再次企出嚟？","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:59:31.000Z","uid":13388,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0166009bac8214d53d1b297b2caaad84776d0aeb","tid":1555422,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"今次係第三次再開post<br />\n<br />\n希望可以推得上去啦<br />\n我有sd去公務員secrets<br />\n但都無post出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當831 同今日勇武手足既事件後<br />\n我覺得除左要打國際線外<br />\n我地自己香港人都要升級<br />\n沖緊涼時 我一直諗點升級？<br />\n<br />\n就係要再展現比香港人 外國人 <br />\n同埋林奠中共呢個恐殘暴權比佢地知道<br />\n我地香港人對林奠你做埋d下三流既行為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔接受</span><br />\n同埋要證明比大家睇 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地團結一致</span><br />\n<br />\n我記得612 616 618 之後<br />\n有好多公務員都索聯署信同集會 <br />\n表達對五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n所以當林奠所謂既撤回 同恐殘既軍政府<br />\n有公務員手足發夢被捕<br />\n同埋有傳既打死香港市民同埋輪姦女義士<br />\n<br />\n希望你地再一次話比政府知<br />\n我地絕對唔會屈服<br />\n<br />\n想係度求求各位公務員 出一出一次聲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武要團結<br />\n<br />\n利伸 發夢成日係中排食煙既手足上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3/9/2019"},{"pid":"2912e2ae8ce0b400f79328d97be46ddc1ad4af3c","tid":1555422,"uid":263289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0166009bac8214d53d1b297b2caaad84776d0aeb","tid":1555422,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:49:21.000Z","msg":"今次係第三次再開post<br /